text: Elizabeth McVeigh (née Paton) (born 8 November 1952) is a British rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:British female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
